[LFM2.5-1.2B-Thinking](https://huggingface.co/LiquidAI/LFM2.5-1.2B-Thinking)
by [Liquid AI, Inc.](https://www.liquid.ai/), licensed under the
**LFM Open License v1.0**.

Key terms of the LFM Open License:
